## EMG Save

```elixir
# --- V10.2 DICTIONARY CHECKPOINT SAVER ---
# Run this after stopping a burn to save the current 'Imagination' Brain
checkpoint_path = Path.join(File.cwd!(), "v10_dictionary_brain.bin")

brain_map = %{
  e: f_e,
  a1: f_a1,
  f1: f_f1,
  a2: f_a2,
  f2: f_f2,
  lmw: f_lmw,
  lmb: f_lmb
}

File.write!(checkpoint_path, :erlang.term_to_binary(brain_map))
IO.puts("💾 Dictionary Brain saved to #{checkpoint_path}")
